docs {
  ## Get Plugin Info

  Returns basic plugin metadata. No parameters required.

  **Expected Response:**
  ```json
  {
    "name": "Segment Reporting",
    "version": "1.0.0.0",
    "description": "..."
  }
  ```

  **Acceptance Criteria:**
  - ✅ Returns plugin name
  - ✅ Returns version string
  - ✅ Returns description
  - ✅ Requires admin authentication
}
